,"quote":{"pid":"5478c05b2a2d39c95310ffceffdc5e2442719d7b","tid":804842,"uid":37596,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:28:42.000Z","msg":"洩露國家機密<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:35:57.000Z","msg":"小災難就捂住<br />\n大災難就緊係喪事當喜事辦，發下國難財啦<br />\n啲偽人開始出聲，應該係準備籌款<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b35b5543193b080290464c63dc19247328327cce","tid":804842,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:36:03.000Z","msg":"淋病原本諗住港豬澳, 高鐵同沙中線要埋單,<br />\n荷包d 錢慳住洗<br />\n側側膊扮無事唔使捐<br />\n而家唔得喇, 比佢篤爆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36abd5d21e9edb09f9ba7f8ef46f7efc72e04ed0","tid":804842,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ddb88cda2419be2611b2d674ada087d9de42fdd","tid":804842,"uid":20816,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:25:33.000Z","msg":"cctvb好似無提及"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:36:22.000Z","msg":"有報水災<br />\n不過台灣"},{"pid":"724f636868346597e5ad371fccd3fa9063b95e28","tid":804842,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:36:51.000Z","msg":"慘囉 以後可能冇得撈"},{"pid":"aa7e4e073409a7e1d1d1fdbd982f364667bb4af9","tid":804842,"uid":56999,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:36:55.000Z","msg":"其中張馨予詢問「哪裡有正規有效的渠道可以捐獻物資？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n波大無腦<br />\n<br />\n呢條傻閪即係話官方渠無効<br />\n雖然係事實，但講出黎都係要拉"},{"pid":"ef54c7a74bb521868ece04f144d2904680b1e909","tid":804842,"uid":16676,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:45:21.000Z","msg":"120萬<br />\n一人比1000 即係12億<br />\n今次胃口唔細喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8319b28db5c8f96c45f0619622da6